  <brief_title>Interest of Re-oxygenation After Inhalation of 50% Nitrous Oxide / 50% Oxygen Premix in Dental Cares</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of a Kalinox's Administration Protocol for Dental Cares : Interest of Re-oxygenation and Pollution Control</official_title>
