  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The usefulness of re-oxygenation after inhalation of 50% nitrous oxide and 50% oxygen premix
      (Kalinox 170 bar) during dental care is studied and the pollution resulting from
      administration of Kalinox is also investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
